@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fwbksi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((0.61 * wp.sin(tmp + 0.90)) * wp.abs((v1 + 0.05 + v0 + 0.72)))
    v2 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.00 - v1 + 0.35)) * (0.19 + wp.exp(v0 + 0.34)))
    v0 = (v2 / wp.cos((v2 + 0.70 * v1 + 0.42)))
    v1 = (v0 - ((v1 + 0.80 / v1 + 0.71) + v0))
    v0 = ((v1 / (tmp + 0.25 - v2 + 0.38)) + (wp.sin(tmp + 0.01) * wp.cos(v0 + 0.28)))
    tmp = 0.99
    v0 = 0.55
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.exp(v2 + 0.94) - wp.cos(v2 + 0.09)))
    data[tid] = v0
